{"tid":1249742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日返工，有幾個同事問我...","createTime":"2019-06-21T20:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T13:48:37.000Z","uid":86755,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56b8a5e17a9a2b5e94763b39584bca7357da6826","tid":1249742,"uid":86755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日返工無啦啦有幾個同事來問我 &ldquo;How do you feel about the extradition law to China?&rdquo; &ldquo;What about the trade war with China, like Huawei?&rdquo; &ldquo;Didn&rsquo;t 10% of the entire population in Hong Kong came out to a protest to against the law&rdquo; 等等，我聽到真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過都有用好中立的角色去同佢地解釋，包括意思例如佢地只去香港觀光，都可以被中國政府控告並轉往中國，佢哋當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為工作上同事全部鬼佬，而且又唔係距離香港近，所以覺得好surprise<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只想帶出一個訊息就係香港人已經好成功地得到好多attention,希望大家可以繼續團結下去，唔好再分化，打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，直至訴求真正得到回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9600ea9d7823546e416f3d603485c405ef18814f","tid":1249742,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:11:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57abf53960b7513f41fc43663bf472ecc58e7f16","tid":1249742,"uid":266983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"岩，<br />\n我前日番工同vendor support 用teamviewer 幫client 做野，<br />\n佢臨尾一句問我有冇去遊行，<br />\n又話I wish I was there <br />\n媽啊真係好感動啊<br />\n<br />\n佢幾年前因為工作關係<br />\n第一次黎香港做野<br />\n係佢言語之間<br />\n我feel到佢其實好關心香港"},{"pid":"506f7226341fff9596c5df44aaa53fae46df09bb","tid":1249742,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:34:20.000Z","msg":"Sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />this way pls"},{"pid":"d6f7072d0bd016ac77201709e817a7eb86a8a355","tid":1249742,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"開咗實彈喇sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782a0ed043c44fb5ddbdd6a96f8d83f1d8c9625a","tid":1249742,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:43:57.000Z","msg":"好似有人想搵你訓練咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1820361/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1820361/page/2</a><br />\n同埋香港會不會就變卡廷？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1819878/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1819878/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"31c6a0cacd2ced3e5f1773f884bdef09ca803627","tid":1249742,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T08:09:09.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621e5d43577cdf3ca320b400099c77612227d088","tid":1249742,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"this way plz"}]}